Syntax: receive

Receive is used in any of the various post offices around the land to
receive mail that is waiting for you.  You must be in the presence of
a postmaster (in the post office) for this to work.  Most major towns
have a post office.

The <h> mailing system is compliments of Rasmussen from the now
defunct CircleMUD and also of the now defunct JediMUD.

See Also: CHECK, MAIL
